==Description==

The [[Image:Curves_ZebraTool.svg|24px]] [[Curves_ZebraTool|Curves ZebraTool]] tool creates a Zebra texture for surface inspection.

==Usage==

# Select the surface to be tested
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:Curves_ZebraTool.svg|16px]] [[Curves_ZebraTool|ZebraTool]]}} button
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Surfaces → [[Image:Curves_ZebraTool.svg|16px]] ZebraTool}} option from the menu
# Optionally change parameters in the '''Zebra Stripes Tool''' [[Task_panel|Task panel]].
# Press any button {{Button|OK}}, {{Button|Cancel}}, or {{Button|Quit}} to finish and exit the tool.

==Parameters==

* '''Black Stripes Width''': Changes the width of the black stripes.
* '''Scale''': Scales the Zebra stripes.
* '''Rotation''': Rotates the Zebra stripes.

==Notes==

This tool is for visual inspection only, it doesn't create any object.


